00:20:50.269 --> 00:20:51.810
This is not something
people are used

00:20:51.810 --> 00:20:53.550
to, used to seeing
or understanding

00:20:53.550 --> 00:20:55.110
or even feeling is safe.

00:20:55.110 --> 00:20:57.510
So they saw this and
