00:21:00.120 --> 00:21:01.530
How can they
conceive of why this

00:21:01.530 --> 00:21:03.904
has merit when it's the first
time they've seen something

00:21:03.904 --> 00:21:06.390
like it.

00:21:06.390 --> 00:21:07.840
A more recent example.

00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:11.480
I know that I have forced all of
you to go back in time to ages

00:21:11.480 --> 00:21:12.730
when there was no electricity.

00:21:12.730 --> 00:21:13.770
So I'm going to give
you an example that's

00:21:13.770 --> 00:21:15.300
a little bit more
recent, actually,

00:21:15.300 --> 00:21:16.425
in the time of electricity.

00:21:16.425 --> 00:21:18.600
I'm going to show you
a picture of a device,

00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:21.420
a prototype, a prototype
of a device that's

00:21:21.420 --> 00:21:24.180
one of the most important
inventions in the last 50

00:21:24.180 --> 00:21:26.729
years, and I want to see if
