So two people raised their hand.

00:22:00.033 --> 00:22:01.650
Do have still the guess?

00:22:01.650 --> 00:22:02.150
Anybody?

00:22:02.150 --> 00:22:04.585
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]
