00:33:43.403 --> 00:33:45.110
It's about false constraints.

00:33:45.110 --> 00:33:47.180
The whole notion here
is that no one told you

00:33:47.180 --> 00:33:50.750
in solving the problem that you
couldn't work outside the box.

00:33:50.750 --> 00:33:53.180
We presume it.

00:33:53.180 --> 00:33:56.510
To live in society, we
presume lots of constraints.

00:33:56.510 --> 00:33:58.280
When you came in this
room, none of you

00:33:58.280 --> 00:34:01.490
sat down up here, next to me.

00:34:01.490 --> 00:34:04.176
None of you were standing up in
