00:37:10.722 --> 00:37:12.180
If you're pitching
something that's

00:37:12.180 --> 00:37:14.650
been done before that you
know is going to work,

00:37:14.650 --> 00:37:16.020
there's not much risk there.

00:37:16.020 --> 00:37:17.340
We're talking about progress.

00:37:17.340 --> 00:37:18.881
We're talking about
good ideas, we're

00:37:18.881 --> 00:37:20.350
