00:37:20.350 --> 00:37:21.090
There's going to be risk there.

00:37:21.090 --> 00:37:22.840
You're going to be
going into the unknown.

00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:25.550
And part of what makes a
good team or a good boss

00:37:25.550 --> 00:37:27.870
are people who make you
feel comfortable offering up

00:37:27.870 --> 00:37:29.310
things that might not work.

00:37:29.310 --> 00:37:31.260
There's some room and
